Layer	                                               Purpose	                                                                                    Thread Context
===================================================================================================================================================================================
UI / RecyclerView binding	                           Shows visible posters (posterImageView.load())	                                            Main thread (UI)
Preloading system	                                   Decodes & caches off-screen posters	                                                        Background (Dispatchers.IO)
Coil’s internal threads	                               Network fetch, decode, and transform	                                                        Coil’s own I/O + decode thread pools



[Main Thread] ──► RecyclerView binds
                 │
                 ├─► posterImageView.load() → Coil (background fetch + decode) → back to main to draw
                 │
                 └─► emits focus position → preloadThrottle

[Dispatchers.IO] ──► debounce(400ms) → preloadRange()
                     │
                     └─► Coil.enqueue(bgRequest) → decode + cache (stays here)









